formation 
Behavior: global 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Returns the current formation of a group.  
Syntax:  
 String = formation grp 
Parameters: 
grp: Object or Group 
Return Value: 
 String -  returns either "COLUMN", "STAG COLUMN", "WEDGE", "ECH LEFT", "ECH RIGHT", "VEE" or "LINE"